<oops:Pitfall>
<oops:Code>P22</oops:Code><oops:Name>Using different naming conventions in the ontology</oops:Name>
<oops:Description>The ontology elements are not named following the same convention (for example CamelCase or use of delimiters as &quot;-&quot; or &quot;_&quot;) . Some notions about naming conventions are provided in [2].	</oops:Description>
<oops:Importance>Minor</oops:Importance>
